Event Management System

A Django REST API for managing events, user registrations, and authentication. Users can sign up, log in, browse events, register, and cancel registrations. Includes an admin panel for managing users, events, and registrations.

Key Features

User authentication with token-based login

Create, view, and manage events

Event registration with capacity checks and cancellation

Admin panel for managing users, events, and registrations

REST API endpoints for frontend or mobile integration

Setup
git clone https://github.com/Usman-54/CodeAlpha_Tasks.git
cd CodeAlpha_Tasks
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py createsuperuser
python manage.py runserver


Admin panel: http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/

API Endpoints

/signup/ – Register new user

/login/ – User login

/events/ – List/Create events

/events/<id>/ – Event details

/events/<id>/register/ – Register for an event

/registrations/ – User registrations

/registrations/<id>/cancel/ – Cancel registration
